OL,3,CJersey Gambling Commission report
OL,4,Ccalls for on-island treatment centre
OL,6,FThe Chairman of the Jersey Gambling
OL,7,FCommission is calling on the
OL,8,Fgovernment to provide a treatment
OL,9,Fservice for gambling addiction on
OL,10,Fisland.
OL,12,FThe Commission released its 2023
OL,13,Fannual report on Friday 26 July that
OL,14,Fhighlights gambling trends, the
OL,15,FCommission's responsibilities, and its
OL,16,Ffinancial situation.
OL,18,FOne topic mentioned throughout the
OL,19,Freport was the need for dedicated on-
OL,20,Fisland support.
