OL,3,CJersey Gambling Commission report
OL,4,Ccalls for on-island treatment centre
OL,6,FChairman Cyril Whelan wrote: "Last
OL,7,Fyear, the Commission came within days
OL,8,Fof signing a contract with a major
OL,9,Foverseas treatment specialist to
OL,10,Festablish a service, when the other
OL,11,Fparty undertook a strategic review and
OL,12,Fchanged course, choosing to focus on
OL,13,Fits domestic work.
OL,15,F"This was a cruel blow after expending
OL,16,Fa significant amount of time and money
OL,17,Fgetting to what looked like the finish
OL,18,Fline, only to have the prize snatched
OL,19,Faway at the last moment."
