OL,3,CJersey Gambling Commission report
OL,4,Ccalls for on-island treatment centre
OL,6,FThe Commission does have a Social
OL,7,FResponsibility Fund that is raised
OL,8,Fthrough payments through those who
OL,9,Fhold gambling licences.
OL,11,FWhile the Fund raised an additional
OL,12,F#14,000 in 2023 than the year before,
OL,13,Fthe Commission states it is "not
OL,14,Fsufficient (to) deliver significant
OL,15,Flong-term projects, such as the
OL,16,Fdelivery of an on-Island treatment and
OL,17,Fcounselling service."
OL,19,FHowever, the report maintains that the
OL,20,FCommission now works positively with
OL,21,FMinisters to find solutions.
