OL,3,CJersey Gambling Commission report
OL,4,Ccalls for on-island treatment centre
OL,6,FAccording to the Commission, two
OL,7,Findividuals received travel and
OL,8,Faccommodation financial support to
OL,9,Freceive gambling addiction treatment
OL,10,Fin the UK.
OL,12,FThe Commission also admitted "the
OL,13,Fnumber of people seeking help will
OL,14,Falways be low" but added that if
OL,15,Ffunded services can help just one
OL,16,FIslander, then any support is
OL,17,F"worthwhile".
