OL,3,CJersey Gambling Commission report
OL,4,Ccalls for on-island treatment centre
OL,6,FThe report states: "The Commission
OL,7,Fcontinues to offer support to
OL,8,FIslanders needing to travel to the UK
OL,9,Fin order to receive in-house
OL,10,Fcounselling treatment and continues to
OL,11,Fwork with a number of providers to
OL,12,Fensure dedicated support is available
OL,13,Ffor Jersey residents."
